[size=140][u]Player POI[/u][/size]

Implementation of player POI (point of interest) system, allowing players to create and manage custom POIs in on the map and in space.

[size=130][u]Features[/u][/size]
[list]
[*] [b]Creation of custom POIs[/b] on the map at any location.
[*] [b]Assignment of POIs to objects[/b] on map or in space (non player stations and gates).
[*] [b]Automatic name generation[/b] for POIs based on the assigned object or location.
[*] [b]Automatic POI assignment[/b] to found abandoned ships and lockboxes (if configured).
[*] [b]POI management tab[/b] in the Property Owned Information.
[*] [b]Context menu[/b] for POIs in space and on the map, allowing to rename or self-destruct POIs.
[*] [b]Optimized rename window location[/b] to be close to the selected POI.
[/list]
