[size=125][u]Limitations[/u][/size]
[list]
[*] As there is standard [b]Rename[/b] window is used for renaming POIs, there is a standard game limitation on the name length that can be applied.
[*] [b]POI[/b] is not attached to the assigned object, so there is no limitation on count of [b]POIs[/b] that can be assigned to the same object, but also it means that if the assigned object is moved or destroyed, the [b]POI[/b] will remain in its original location and will not be updated or removed.
[/list]
