And here is how the list of [b]POIs[/b] looks like after the [b]POI[/b] has been self-destructed:

[spoiler][img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chemodun/X4-PlayerPOI/refs/heads/main/docs/images/poi_tab_after_self_destruct.png[/img][/spoiler]

